flowchart LR
    U[User Speech Input] --> VAD[VAD / Denoise]
    VAD --> ASR[ASR Engine<br/>Streaming RNN-T/CTC]
    ASR --> CONF[Token Confidence + Uncertainty]
    CONF --> DIAG[Pronunciation and Prosody Scoring<br/>GOP / Stress / Intonation / Pause]
    DIAG --> LLM[LLM Tutor Core<br/>SFT + Preference Optimization]
    KB[Policy and Curriculum KB] --> RAG[RAG Retriever]
    RAG --> LLM
    LLM --> AGENT[Dialogue Manager / Agent Orchestration]
    AGENT --> MEM[Long-term Learner Memory]
    MEM --> AGENT
    AGENT --> UI[Feedback + Next Task + Explanation]
    UI --> U
    AGENT --> HUMAN[Teacher Override / Escalation]
